      "content": "It sounds like you are experiencing an intense sense of loss regarding your identity and purpose, which can feel overwhelming at first. While that feeling that a part of you has died is very realistic in the moment, your capacity to feel and connect remains intact on a human level, even if the creative outlet has shifted. I encourage you to reach out to a mental health professional who can help you explore these feelings of emptiness without judgment.",
      "source": "target",
